oes all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"https://redrambles.blog//wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!\r\n\r\nClick on this to download the awesome <a href=\"https://redrambles.blog//wp-content/uploads/2015/09/WebDesignPackages1.pdf\">WebDesignPackages</a>!\r\n\r\n[slider id=\'47500\' name=\'Slider 1\' size=\'full\']','Sample Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2015-12-30 01:59:20','2015-12-30 01:59:20','',14,'https://redrambles.blog//14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(47502,1,'2015-12-31 19:24:30','2015-12-31 19:24:30','<p>I’m a student of all things web development and hack away at various code projects with the passion of a zealot. I\'m also a mom of a small pack of minions who will one day do my bidding. (For now, I\'m working on our family grocery shopping time NOT shaving years off of my life.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During my off-parent duties, when I’m not crafting code (which in fairness - is most of the time), I like to sing, play the mandolin, curl up with a good sci-fi/fantasy book or take long walks with my dogs.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"social-btns\">\r\n<a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/redrambles/\" class=\"soc-icon tw\"></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/redramblesAnn/\" class=\"soc-icon fb\"></a>\r\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"soc-icon ln\"></a>\r\n<a href=\"#\" class=\"soc-icon db\"></a>\r\n</div>','Hi, I\'m Ann.I love building websites.','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-revision-v1','','','2015-12-31 19:24:30','2015-12-31 19:24:30','',4,'https://redrambles.blog//4-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(47503,1,'2016-01-01 19:01:18','2016-01-01 19:01:18','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-47483 alignleft\" src=\"https://redrambles.blog//wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_2478-297x300.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_2478\" w