> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!\r\n\r\nClick on this to download the awesome <a href=\"https://redrambles.blog//wp-content/uploads/2015/09/WebDesignPackages1.pdf\">WebDesignPackages</a>!','Sample Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','14-revision-v1','','','2016-01-18 19:27:37','2016-01-18 19:27:37','',14,'https://redrambles.blog//14-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(47524,1,'2016-01-19 02:19:12','2016-01-19 02:19:12','','Slideshow test','','publish','closed','closed','','slideshow-test','','','2016-01-19 02:19:12','2016-01-19 02:19:12','',0,'https://redrambles.blog//?post_type=slideshow&#038;p=47524',0,'slideshow','',0),(47525,1,'2016-01-19 02:20:48','2016-01-19 02:20:48','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JLyvy8SXEPE\r\n\r\nWelcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging! Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging! Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging! Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging! Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging! Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!\r\n\r\nWelcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!\r\n\r\nHere is a slideshow for no reason at all!\r\n\r\n[slideshow_deploy id=\'47524\']','Hello world!','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2016-01-19 02:20:48','2016-01-19 02:20:48','',13,'https://redrambles.blog//13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(47526,1,'2016-01-19 02:25:12','2016-01-19 02:25:12','','Large slideshow test','','publish','closed','closed','','large-slideshow-test','','','2016-01-19 02:25:12','2016-01-19 02:25:12','',0,'https://redrambles.blog//?post_type=slideshow&#038;p=47526',0,'slideshow','',0),(47527,1,'2016-01-19 02:25:50','2016-01-19 02:25:50','<ul>Here i