otham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"https://redrambles.blog//wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun! Lots, lots of fun!\r\n\r\n[cta-simple tel=\"514-497-3725\" email=\"a.cascarano@gmail.com\"]','Test Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2017-02-02 16:38:09','2017-02-02 16:38:09','',2,'https://redrambles.blog//2-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(47787,1,'2017-02-24 19:19:54','2017-02-24 19:19:54','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-47483 alignleft\" src=\"https://redrambles.blog//wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_2478-297x300.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_2478\" width=\"247\" height=\"250\" />Hide when guests come over <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">meowzer!</span> or <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">unwrap toilet paper</span> <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">spread kitty litter all over house</span>. Inspect anything brought into the house <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">love to play with owner\'s hair tie</span> <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">drink water out of the faucet</span> <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">poop on grasses</span> <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">if it smells like fish eat as much as you wish</span>. Who\'s the baby. Why must they do that inspect anything brought into the house. <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">Ears back wide eyed</span> sun bathe, yet <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">lick the plastic bag</span> so <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">destroy the blinds</span> so run in circles. Find something else more interesting chew iPad power cord, but <span class=\"tooltiplink\" title=\"By: Anonymous \">spread kitty litter all over house</span> <sp